{"tid":1519732,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"（831淺水灣BE WATER）如果決定唔送頭又想爬山的義士請進！","createTime":"2019-08-30T15:45:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-30T15:56:34.000Z","uid":8834,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"d393856ab92ca1f0f4303cd329ddf897ede37699","tid":1519732,"uid":8834,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T15:45:18.000Z","msg":"香港好大獲，我祈禱問耶穌，佢話明天需要奇招。<br />\n<br />\n佢話聽左好多日be water，叫大家不如明天真係去沙灘，真心。BE WATER精神其實由摩西過紅海開始，我地聽日就去be water吧。沙灘呢個環境好specific，一定安全，嚇下班有錢佬，史無前例，畫面有趣，外媒實報！其實地方真係冇所謂，遍地開花，人數最緊要，可以耶穌話明天差唔多鐘數沙灘見，be water，阿門。"},{"pid":"6f942eb1dce7c3450b8591945d5d90a43a25439a","tid":1519732,"uid":8834,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T15:45:26.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b644aed7029e891f0975a6b451199fbd22734f9a","tid":1519732,"uid":8834,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T15:45:37.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6cc62cadd619a9612b0dc92724ee14405c72642d","tid":1519732,"uid":8834,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T15:47:22.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0ea385fb0573090259164d317e0c74b2ba06cd74","tid":1519732,"uid":8834,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T15:48:22.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"95489f2028ae4e02a02b5df67a855728b551664f","tid":1519732,"uid":8834,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T15:48:32.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7429097cdd0f6e8ca0a4846e35024dfbcacd5124","tid":1519732,"uid":204194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T15:49:30.000Z","msg":"探人?"},{"pid":"5da5f913ae5a703c8f8564d0152deba4341d928d","tid":1519732,"uid":33930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T15:50:50.000Z","msg":"幾句講哂<br />\n831宗教集會<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">901 1點鐘 機場見</span></span><br />\n92大三罷<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OvNBCkd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=htt